org.sql: SELECT projects.* FROM projects WHERE projects.lft < 15 AND projects.rgt > 16 AND projects.status <> 9 AND projects.is_public = True AND projects.id NOT IN (SELECT project_id FROM members WHERE user_id IN (6, 13)) ORDER BY projects.lft ASC
